", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual abuse\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"the hands\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1528}, {\"ngram\": \"her childhood coach\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"a trusted family friend\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"16 years\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"12 to 16 years\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back then,Time magazinesummarized the outcome: \\\"Harrison's mother eventually found out about the abuse, through one of her daughter's friends, and reported [Daniel] Doyle to the police.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Harrison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.568193069808425e-17, \"text\": \"Harrison\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Harrison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Harrison\"}, {\"begin\": 1823, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Conan_Doyle\", \"score\": 0.7339608176385028, \"rank\": 0.36247055151684954, \"text\": \"Doyle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Conan_Doyle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arthur_Conan_Doyle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Time\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"her daughter's friends\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In November 2007, Doyle pleaded guilty to a count of 'engaging in illicit sexual conduct in a foreign place.'\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1862, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia