s of any form of abuse or past entrapments can take to attain recovery, freedom, and one's dreams.\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2098, \"end\": 2103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"her triumph\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"tragedy\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"a path\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"victims\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"any form\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"abuse\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"entrapments\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"one's dreams\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are a few of those inspirational lessons that her life and actions still teach and remind us: (1) Do not let being a victim define or paralyze you anymore than it already has tried; rather, use it as a catalyst to grow, overcome, and fuel victory.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those inspirational lessons\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"actions\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"a victim define\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"a catalyst\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheU.K.\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheU.K.\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'s Guardianreported how Kayla said everything in her life - the good, the bad, and the ugly - was used to help her overcome and reach her goals: \\\"Kind of just reflecting back on my life.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Guardianreported\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"Kayla\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"the good\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2623}, {\"ngram\": \"her goals\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything it's taken to get here, and everything that I have gone through.\\\"\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kayla reminded me of a critical fact in personal growth: Our past can be the fire for victory in our present; it does not have to paralyze and enslave you.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kayla\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2825}, {\"ngram\": \"a critical fact\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"personal growth\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"Our past\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"the fire\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2913}, {\"ngram\": \"our present\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Triumph over trauma can be our greatest achievement because it helps us in myriad ways.\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Triumph\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"trauma\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"our greatest achievement\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3027}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"myriad ways\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her own words, Kayla said her journey \\\"is proof that you are only a victim if you allow yourself to be.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3083, \"end\": 3088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own words\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3081}, {\"ngram\": \"her journey\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3105}, {\"ngram\": \"proof\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"only a victim\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing can stop you.\\\"\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(2) Surround yourself with people who will push -and sometimes even pull - you toward healing, wholeness, and your goals.\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"healing\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"wholeness\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"your goals\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kayla and her mother wisely knew that she alone could not overcome her assailant's effects or achieve her athletic dreams, so they searched far and wide for reputable, safe, and healthy coaches.\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kayla\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3339}, {\"ngram\": \"her assailant's effects\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"her athletic dreams\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3440}, {\"ngram\": \"reputable, safe, and healthy coaches\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They discovered them in the two-time Olympic medal winner, Jimmy Pedro Jr., and his father, who together got Kayla into therapy, rebuilt her confidence, and trained her to be a judo champion.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3574, \"end\": 3585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jimmy Pedro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the two-time Olympic medal winner\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3605}, {\"ngram\": \"Kayla\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3642}, {\"ngram\": \"her confidence\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"a judo champion\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as the instructors in ourKICKSTART KIDSprogram serve as positive mentors and models for their martial arts students, the Pedros served as catalysts for change for Kayla.\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3876, \"end\": 3881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the instructors\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3731}, {\"ngram\": \"ourKICKSTART KIDSprogram\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3759}, {\"ngram\": \"positive mentors\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"models\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3796}, {\"ngram\": \"their martial arts students\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3828}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pedros\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3840}, {\"ngram\": \"catalysts\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3860}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, at age of 16, she moved in with 10 other of Pedro's students, who all lived in the safety of the same apartment.\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3931, \"end\": 3936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_II_of_Brazil\", \"score\": 0.999999394613225, \"rank\": 5.222414688174112e-07, \"text\": \"Pedro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_II_of_Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_II_of_Brazil\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3893}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 3976}, {\"ngram\": \"the same apartment\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 3998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you think Kayla had an inherent Olympic mindset when she arrived, think again.\", \"from\": 4001, \"to\": 4086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4018, \"end\": 4023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an inherent Olympic mindset\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, Time reported how Jimmy Pedro Jr. explained just how low Kayla was when she arrived under their tutelage: \\\"She was not in a good state of mind.\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4113, \"end\": 4124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jimmy Pedro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\"}, {\"begin\": 4152, \"end\": 4157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Time\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4099}, {\"ngram\": \"their tutelage\", \"from\": 4185, \"to\": 4199}, {\"ngram\": \"a good state\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4229}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 4233, \"to\": 4237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was somebody who had no self-esteem.\", \"from\": 4239, \"to\": 4279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"no self-esteem\", \"from\": 4264, \"to\": 4278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not know, really, right from wrong.\", \"from\": 4280, \"to\": 4323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wrong\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was somebody who did not know if she wanted to go on with life or not.\\\"\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4340}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pedro recounted how once he even discovered Harrison on the roof of a two-story apartment, wondering whether or not she should jump.\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4401, \"end\": 4406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_II_of_Brazil\", \"score\": 0.999999394613225, \"rank\": 5.222414688174112e-07, \"text\": \"Pedro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_II_of_Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_II_of_Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 4445, \"end\": 4453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Harrison\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.568193069808425e-17, \"text\": \"Harrison\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Harrison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Harrison\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4465}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-story apartment\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was just a very, very, very low point.\\\"\", \"from\": 4534, \"to\": 4577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a very, very, very low point\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kayla even confessed just how low she was and how pivotal the help of the Pedros and other teammates were during this critical time, when her past even robbed her of the joy of her sport: \\\"I hated judo.\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kayla\", \"from\": 4579, \"to\": 4584}, {\"ngram\": \"the help\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4645}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pedros\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4659}, {\"ngram\": \"other teammates\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4679}, {\"ngram\": \"this critical time\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4710}, {\"ngram\": \"her past\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4725}, {\"ngram\": \"the joy\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4752}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4765}, {\"ngram\": \"judo\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hated the Pedros.\", \"from\": 4782, \"to\": 4801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Pedros\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not want to be the strong girl.\", \"from\": 4802, \"to\": 4839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the strong girl\", \"from\": 4823, \"to\": 4838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not want to be the golden girl, I did not want to be the one who overcame everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 4840, \"to\": 4932, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the golden girl\", \"from\": 4861, \"to\": 4876}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 4930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, in time, the Pedros and Kayla's fellow judo students encouraged her not to give up.\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 5022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4963, \"end\": 4968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4942, \"to\": 4946}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pedros\", \"from\": 4948, \"to\": 4958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She reflected, \\\"That's why I owe all of this to the Pedros, to my teammates.\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Pedros\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are the ones who got me out of bed in the morning and said, 'We are going to lift.'\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 5110, \"to\": 5118}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5140}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are the ones who picked me off the mat when I was crying and wanted to quit.\", \"from\": 5190, \"to\": 5271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 5199, \"to\": 5207}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat\", \"from\": 5226, \"to\": 5233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am forever grateful to them for that.\\\"\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a fact in becoming a champion: Those who are around you can define your success, or your path to it.\", \"from\": 5314, \"to\": 5419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fact\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5325}, {\"ngram\": \"a champion\", \"from\": 5338, \"to\": 5348}, {\"ngram\": \"your success\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5398}, {\"ngram\": \"your path\", \"from\": 5403, \"to\": 5412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your environment will shape you, for better or worse - you can count on it.\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your environment\", \"from\": 5420, \"to\": 5436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So let your closest friends and colleagues be champions of your improvement.\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your closest friends\", \"from\": 5503, \"to\": 5523}, {\"ngram\": \"colleagues\", \"from\": 5528, \"to\": 5538}, {\"ngram\": \"champions\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5551}, {\"ngram\": \"your improvement\", \"from\": 5555, \"to\": 5571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the magnet states on the refrigerator ofCatherine McCalla licensed marriage and family therapist - as well as sexual-abuse victim and overcomer herself - and a passionate advocate and educator of victims of child abuse: \\\"There are people who take the heart out of you, and there are people who put it back.\\\"\", \"from\": 5574, \"to\": 5884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5627, \"end\": 5634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McCalla,_Alabama\", \"score\": 0.9740280158145314, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"McCalla\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McCalla,_Alabama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McCalla,_Alabama\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the magnet states\", \"from\": 5577, \"to\": 5594}, {\"ngram\": \"marriage and family therapist\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5673}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual-abuse victim\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5706}, {\"ngram\": \"a passionate advocate\", \"from\": 5735, \"to\": 5756}, {\"ngram\": \"educator\", \"from\": 5761, \"to\": 5769}, {\"ngram\": \"victims\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5780}, {\"ngram\": \"child abuse\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5795}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5808, \"to\": 5814}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 5824, 