, {\"sentence\": \"She explained: \\\"It wasn't one particular moment.\", \"from\": 6772, \"to\": 6820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one particular moment\", \"from\": 6798, \"to\": 6819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a collection of moments.\", \"from\": 6821, \"to\": 6852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a collection\", \"from\": 6828, \"to\": 6840}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was my teammates picking me up and making me go to practice and making me go to lifting.\", \"from\": 6853, \"to\": 6944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 6860, \"to\": 6872}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 6907, \"to\": 6915}, {\"ngram\": \"lifting\", \"from\": 6936, \"to\": 6943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Jimmy getting me back in school and me going to see a therapist.\", \"from\": 6945, \"to\": 7016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jimmy\", \"from\": 6952, \"to\": 6957}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 6977, \"to\": 6983}, {\"ngram\": \"a therapist\", \"from\": 7004, \"to\": 7015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And me sort of collecting the pieces of my life and putting them back together.\\\"\", \"from\": 7017, \"to\": 7097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pieces\", \"from\": 7043, \"to\": 7053}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 7057, \"to\": 7064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's exactly what Kayla has done and been doing the last 10 years as she now offers others help through her \\\"Fearless Foundation\\\" and her insightful and powerful book, \\\"Fighting Back: What an Olympic Champion's Story Can Teach Us about Recognizing and Preventing Child Sexual Abuse - and Helping Kids Recover.\\\"\", \"from\": 7099, \"to\": 7411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7119, \"end\": 7124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 7106, \"to\": 7118}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 10 years\", \"from\": 7149, \"to\": 7166}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 7185, \"to\": 7191}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"Fearless Foundation\", \"from\": 7205, \"to\": 7229}, {\"ngram\": \"her insightful and powerful book\", \"from\": 7235, \"to\": 7267}, {\"ngram\": \"What an Olympic Champion's Story\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7317}, {\"ngram\": \"Us\", \"from\": 7328, \"to\": 7330}, {\"ngram\": \"Child Sexual Abuse\", \"from\": 7364, \"to\": 7382}, {\"ngram\": \"Helping Kids\", \"from\": 7389, \"to\": 7401}, {\"ngram\": \"Recover\", \"from\": 7402, \"to\": 7409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Kayla's proudest accomplishment was becoming the mother of two beautiful children!\", \"from\": 7413, \"to\": 7504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7422, \"end\": 7427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.73492135596717e-40, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mother\", \"from\": 7467, \"to\": 7477}, {\"ngram\": \"two beautiful children\", \"from\": 7481, \"to\": 7503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kayla is vivid proof of what theGood Booksays: \\\"What others mean for harm, God can turn around and use for the good.\\\"\", \"from\": 7506, \"to\": 7623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kayla\", \"from\": 7506, \"to\": 7511}, {\"ngram\": \"vivid proof\", \"from\": 7515, \"to\": 7526}, {\"ngram\": \"what theGood Booksays\", \"from\": 7530, \"to\": 7551}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 7559, \"to\": 7565}, {\"ngram\": \"harm\", \"from\": 7575, \"to\": 7579}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 7581, \"to\": 7584}, {\"ngram\": \"the g